name: complex_lattice_clamp_passthrough_when_in_range
section: lattice-clamp
args: x:Int lo:Int hi:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: When x is between ordered bounds, clamp should return x.
law: (if (fuzz-lte? {lo} {x}) (if (fuzz-lte? {x} {hi}) (= (fuzz-min (fuzz-max {x} {lo}) {hi}) {x}) True) True)
